","msg":"點解會批7.27<br />\n農曆 係 六月廿五<br />\n日值月破 即六月最凶果日<br />\n凡破日 諸事皆不宜<br />\n愚昧再卜算出四個字<br />\n魚死網破<br />\n趟若愚昧卜算相近，即兩邊皆損<br />\n港共政府&amp;黑警就是大贏家<br />\n況誰是魚，誰是網？<br />\n説不定<br />\n<br />\n希望各位再再再三思索<br />\n<br />\n鄉黑不如警察<br />\n不會思慮留手<br />\n黑警又擺明企係佢地果邊<br />\n<br />\n其實最賤就是黑警<br />\n反而發夢去圍警署<br />\n要佢交待無警時份<br />\n直播新聞明明拍到白衣人手持武器都話見唔到？<br />\n新聞片+自拍片都影到不下幾十個打人的暴徒有容有貌<br />\n點解唔去捉人？<br />\n爲何群眾去警署報警，反而落閘龜縮？<br />\n<br />\n希望各位有智之士不要中港共政府陷阱。"},{"pid":"ea423913fc5cae4f95b200aaddeb21314725133a","tid":1361810,"uid":53604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:32:35.000Z","msg":"梁天琦民族黨集會演說逐字稿<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1360262\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1360262</a>"},{"pid":"6b261fe4405938268c8534320817ed63c18fd574","tid":1361810,"uid":53604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:11:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3ef35b887c066be01895fdfaf0516d7797ccaf19","tid":1361810,"uid":53604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:24:24.000Z","msg":"去元郎遊行之前請自備一個哨子<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1363214\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1363214</a>"},{"pid":"adc07ae6e5b363d218ed6efe75086ff9d3770110","tid":1361810,"uid":53604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:34:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u6yA2ngwHPc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Du6yA2ngwHPc&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0LPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=d6fda4a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u6yA2ngwHPc</a>"}]}